Sorry guys and gals, but this is my first ever torrent, and I was getting a headache with my failed attempts, and wrote a poor description.
However, to make amends, here is my description.
I took these photos with my camera at arms length, (a tiny Samsung camera) and was amazed to see the image of my arm reflecting in the eye of the young girl.
Hope you enjoy!
